song. May induce sleep.

Tackle.name: Tackle
Tackle.description:
Charges the foe with a full-
body tackle.

Heal Pulse.name: Heal Pulse
Heal Pulse.description:
Recovers up to half the
target's maximum HP.

Synchronoise.name: Synchronoise
Synchronoise.description:
An odd shock wave that only
damages same-type foes.

Bide.name: Bide
Bide.description:
Endures attack for 2
turns to retaliate double.

Pin Missile.name: Pin Missile
Pin Missile.description:
Sharp pins are fired to
strike 2 to 5 times.

Rototiller.name: Rototiller
Rototiller.description:
Ups the Attack and Sp. Atk
of Grass-type Pokémon.

Tar Shot.name: Tar Shot
Tar Shot.description:
Lowers the foe's Speed and
makes it weak to Fire.

Vital Throw.name: Vital Throw
Vital Throw.description:
Makes the user's move last,
but it never misses.

Rage.name: Rage
Rage.description:
Raises the user's Attack
every time it is hit.

Aqua Cutter.name: Aqua Cutter
Aqua Cutter.description:
Pressurized water cut with a
high critical-hit ratio.

Mean Look.name: Mean Look
Mean Look.description:
Fixes the foe with a mean
look that prevents escape.

Doodle.name: Doodle
Doodle.description:
Changes user's and ally's
Ability into the target's.

Thunder.name: Thunder
Thunder.description:
A lightning attack that may
cause paralysis.

High Horsepower.description:
Slams hard into the foe with
its entire body.

Thousand Waves.description:
Those hit by the wave can
no longer escape.

Bolt Beak.name: Bolt Beak
Bolt Beak.description:
Double power if the user
moves before the target.

Mimic.name: Mimic
Mimic.description:
Copies a move used by the
foe during one battle.

Dragon Breath.description:
Strikes the foe with an
incredible blast of breath.

Thief.name: Thief
Thief.description:
While attacking, it may
steal the foe's held item.

Springtide Storm.description:
Wraps a foe in fierce winds.
Varies with the user's form.

Mountain Gale.description:
Giant chunks of ice damage
the foe. It may flinch.

Role Play.name: Role Play
Role Play.description:
Mimics the target and
copies its special ability.

Celebrate.name: Celebrate
Celebrate.description:
Congratulates you on your
special day.

Gear Up.name: Gear Up
Gear Up.description:
Boosts the attacks of
those with Plus or Minus.

Stun Spore.name: Stun Spore
Stun Spore.description:
Scatters a powder that may
paralyze the foe.

High Jump Kick.description:
A jumping knee kick. If it
misses, the user is hurt.

Blood Moon.name: Blood Moon
Blood Moon.description:
Unleashes the blood moon.
Can't be used twice in a row.

Bramble Barrage.name: Bramble Barrage
Bramble Barrage.description:
User attacks with a flurry 
of brambles. Sets up spikes.

Quick Guard.name: Quick Guard
Quick Guard.description:
Evades priority attacks
for one turn.

Lands Wrath.name: Land's Wrath
Lands Wrath.description:
Gathers the energy of the
land to attack every foe.

Soak.name: Soak
Soak.description:
Sprays water at the foe
making it Water-type.

Flamethrower.name: Flamethrower
Flamethrower.description:
A powerful fire attack that
may inflict a burn.

Taunt.name: Taunt
Taunt.description:
Taunts the foe into only
using attack moves.

Overheat.name: Overheat
Overheat.description:
Allows a full-power attack,
but sharply lowers Sp. Atk.

Bubble.name: Bubble
Bubble.description:
An attack using bubbles.
May lower the foe's Speed.

Seed Bomb.name: Seed Bomb
Seed Bomb.description:
A barrage of hard seeds
is fired at the foe.

Lock On.name: Lock-On
Lock On.description:
Locks on to the foe to
ensure the next move hits.

Accelerock.name: Accelerock
Accelerock.description:
Hits with a high-speed
rock that always goes first.

Branch Poke.name: Branch Poke
Branch Poke.description:
The user pokes the target
with a pointed branch.

Thunder Shock.description:
An electrical attack that
may paralyze the foe.

Iron Tail.name: Iron Tail
Iron Tail.description:
Attacks with a rock-hard
tail. May lower Defense.

Leaf Blade.name: Leaf Blade
Leaf Blade.description:
Slashes with a sharp leaf.
High critical-hit ratio.

Moongeist Beam.description:
A moon-powered beam that
ignores abilities.

Milk Drink.name: Milk Drink
Milk Drink.description:
Recovers up to half the
user's maximum HP.

Aeroblast.name: Aeroblast
Aeroblast.description:
Launches a vacuumed blast.
High critical-hit ratio.

Freeze Dry.name: Freeze-Dry
Freeze Dry.description:
Super effective on Water-
types. May cause frostbite.

Dual Chop.name: Dual Chop
Dual Chop.description:
Attacks with brutal hits
that strike twice.

Echoed Voice.name: Echoed Voice
Echoed Voice.description:
Does more damage every turn
it is used.

Burning Jealousy.description:
Foes that have stats upped
during the turn get burned.

Block.name: Block
Block.description:
Blocks the foe's way to
prevent escape.

Psycho Boost.name: Psycho Boost
Psycho Boost.description:
Allows a full-power attack,
but sharply lowers Sp. Atk.

Blue Flare.name: Blue Flare
Blue Flare.description:
Engulfs the foe in a blue
flame. May inflict a burn.

Low Sweep.name: Low Sweep
Low Sweep.description:
Attacks the foe's legs
lowering its Speed.

Giga Drain.name: Giga Drain
Giga Drain.description:
An attack that steals half
the damage inflicted.

Weather Ball.name: Weather Ball
Weather Ball.description:
The move's type and power
change with the weather.

Double Edge.name: Double-Edge
Double Edge.description:
A life-risking tackle that
also hurts the user.

Toxic.name: Toxic
Toxic.description:
Poisons the foe with an
intensifying toxin.

Purify.name: Purify
Purify.description:
Cures the foe's status
to restore HP.

Sludge Bomb.name: Sludge Bomb
Sludge Bomb.description:
Sludge is hurled to inflict
damage. May also poison.

Lumina Crash.name: Lumina Crash
Lumina Crash.description:
A mind-affecting light
harshly lowers Sp. Def.

Megahorn.name: Megahorn
Megahorn.description:
A brutal ramming attack
using out-thrust horns.

Stored Power.name: Stored Power
Stored Power.description:
The higher the user's stats
the more damage caused.

Teatime.name: Teatime
Teatime.description:
All Pokémon have teatime
and eat their Berries.

Slack Off.name: Slack Off
Slack Off.description:
Slacks off and restores
half the maximum HP.

Final Gambit.name: Final Gambit
Final Gambit.description:
The user faints to damage
the foe equal to its HP.

Rest.name: Rest
Rest.description:
The user sleeps for 2 turns,
restoring HP and status.

Pay Day.name: Pay Day
Pay Day.description:
Throws coins at the foe.
Money is recovered after.

Yawn.name: Yawn
Yawn.description:
Lulls the foe into yawning,
then sleeping next turn.

Multi Attack.name: Multi-Attack
Multi Attack.description:
An attack that changes
with Memories.

Earth Power.name: Earth Power
Earth Power.description:
Makes the ground erupt with
power. May lower Sp. Def.

Dual Wingbeat.description:
User slams the target with
wings and hits twice in a row.

Heal Block.name: Heal Block
Heal Block.description:
Prevents the foe from
recovering any HP.

Energy Ball.name: Energy Ball
Energy Ball.description:
Draws power from nature to
attack. May lower Sp. Def.

Nature Power.name: Nature Power
Nature Power.description:
The type of attack varies
depending on the location.

Egg Bomb.name: Egg Bomb
Egg Bomb.description:
An egg is forcibly hurled at
the foe.

Lunge.name: Lunge
Lunge.description:
Lunges at the foe to lower
its Attack stat.

Flare Blitz.name: Flare Blitz
Flare Blitz.description:
A charge that may burn the
foe. Also hurts the user.

Metal Sound.name: Metal Sound
Metal Sound.description:
Emits a horrible screech
that sharply lowers Sp. Def.

Fillet Away.name: Fillet Away
Fillet Away.description:
Sharply boosts offenses and
Speed by using its own HP.

Volt Tackle.name: Volt Tackle
Volt Tackle.description:
A life-risking tackle that
slightly hurts the user.
